snippet.textDisplay: Ive a lot of questions. First of all, the amount of talent and underground artists we have is immense and when I saw artists like Seedhe Maut  and Achint on the launch, I was damn excited but this just feels really out of place, like far behind expectations and it breaks my heart. The other thing is Ravi Kishan was not even on the stage, as if he has'nt shot and recorded at the same time and it was looking really odd. I'm a huge fan of SM but there talent was underutilised here. Unka lyrical game itna zabardast hai but aisa lag raha tha k kya gaa rahe hain yeh log. Disappointed.
